tmux

Plugins are installed in .local/share/tmux/..
.local/share is a disposable directory

USAGE NOTES

GPT suggests the following type usage

Session = project or genuinely separate mental world.
Window = task branch, Codex run, shell role, log tail, build loop, notes, REPL.
Pane = tightly coupled simultaneous views inside one task.
Server = invisible substrate; do not architect around it unless you have daemon-like requirements.

Furthermore, systemd integration might be effective to achieve persistence independent of graphical session.


TASKS / PROJECTS

Experiment with tmux-notify to indicate when agentic workflows need input or have completed
Change pane border colors. Just one partial border looks out of place
Implement tmux as a systemd user service pre graphical


